org.digijava.module.translation.entity

Class PatcherMessageGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.module.translation.entity.MessageGroup
      • org.digijava.module.translation.entity.PatcherMessageGroup

  • public class PatcherMessageGroup
extends MessageGroup
    Group of messages with same translation key. They also should have same hash key but generated preferably from English translation. Unlike its parent this class is used to patch messages with generated key.
    See Also:
    HashKeyPatch

      • doPutMessage

        protected void doPutMessage(Message message)
        Puts message in the group. This overridden method also generates hash key from message body. For this it uses first message added which may be overwritten only by English message later. So if there is English translation it will be used for key generation, or if there is no English then any other language message will be used.
        Overrides:
        doPutMessage in class MessageGroup
        Parameters:
